{
  "text": "DMF consists in introducing these expansions (1-2) in a weak formulation of the considered vibro-acoustic problem and using the orthogonality properties of the uncoupled modes. For more details on this formulation, the reader can study Ref. [CITATION_1] . The following modal equations are obtained",
  "citation_candidates": [
